13 SECTION 75. TEMPORARY PROVISION--TRIBAL INFRASTRUCTURE
14 BOARD--FUNDING SUFFICIENT TO COMPLETE PROJECTS.--For fiscal
15 years 2026 and 2027, the tribal infrastructure board shall
16 provide up to fifteen percent of available annual funds for
any single project. The board shall make every effort to
17
award funding to qualifying projects in amounts sufficient to
18
complete funding for the projects, after accounting for other
19
funding already secured for those projects.
